1115
00:37:57,199 --> 00:37:58,000
Unbelievable!

1116
00:37:59,599 --> 00:38:01,119
I'm just scared.

1117
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:02,199
Well, if you're scared,

1118
00:38:02,199 --> 00:38:03,440
