1119
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,559
What do you think of me?

1120
00:38:12,599 --> 00:38:13,159
No worries.

1121
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,119
I'll be here with you.

1122
00:38:17,119 --> 00:38:17,719
It'll be okay.

1123
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:51,520
Haowen.

1124
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:54,079
Haowen.

1125
00:39:01,039 --> 00:39:02,000
Jia Haowen!

1126
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:04,559
Honey!

1127
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:05,440
