1167
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,280
Just stay calm.

1168
00:41:03,759 --> 00:41:05,480
Relax, don't be nervous.

1169
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,320
If you're nervous,

1170
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:08,159
